RequestOptions

Configuration specific to the current request.
Type:
  • Object
Properties:
Name Type Description
requestId String User specified request identifier which must be a UUID.
batchSize Number Indicates whether the Power component is present.
userAgent String The size in which the result of a request is to be 'batched' back to the client
evaluationTimeout Number The timeout for the evaluation of the request.
materializeProperties String Indicates whether element properties should be returned or not.
